A. Harding Steerman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A._Harding_Steerman 0 A. Harding Steerman (21 November 1863 - 1947) was an English actor. He is sometimes credited as Harding Steerman. He was born Alfred Harding Treeby Stalman in St Pancras, London and died in Plymouth, Devon. A._Harding_Steerman ( 21 November 1863 - 1947 ) was an_English_actor .
